description:
The 1st Edition of the THRILLING anthology series is here for the taking! This issue is targeting the amazon and thought provoking tales of shock and awe by hot new comic writer, Troy Vevasis and display uniquely designed theme styles from 1960's sci-fi animation, 1970's hand colored, 1980's black and white line-art and modern indie comics influences. amazon Best-selling author and professional comics creator Brad Linder has worked with fellow artists of this title to bring different looks to each of these stories and support an individual experience for the reader from one to the next, just as Troy intended with his signature style of storytelling that is making him climb as someone to watch in the comic industry indie market.

All of these stories come together for a broad spectrum that will reach every's interest, be it sci-fi, action-adventure, fantasy, crime and the paranormal.

If you are looking for something interesting, different and new, this is the way to go!
